1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 57 =

20
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,540
Your Majesty.

21
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:48,660
Cao Yi submitted a proposal for self-impeachment,

22
00:01:49,260 --> 00:01:51,340
asking you to fire him and punish him.

23
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,100
Your Majesty.

24
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:18,180
What about the Cao family...

25
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:21,820
Go on with the surveillance.

26
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,540
Aye.

27
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:50,980
Is that you, Danshu?

28
00:02:52,820 --> 00:02:54,540
I bring you some congee, Your Majesty.

29
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:57,540
If you’re busy with work,

30
00:02:58,260 --> 00:02:59,540
I’ll leave right away

31
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:02,100
and let Liaozi serve you dinner.

32
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:05,860
Come in.

33
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:24,340
Your Majesty.

34
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:48,900
Has Huirou had something to eat?

35
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,300
Yes.

36
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:56,500
I brought her the same congee

37
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:59,140
and saw her have half a bowl of it.

38
00:04:09,060 --> 00:04:09,820
Your Majesty.

39
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:13,620
Let me serve you

40
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:16,820
with medicine and dinner.

41
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:36,060
These proposals,

42
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:39,260
no,

43
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:42,460
I mean the proposals over the past two years.

44
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:45,780
In most of them, officials advised me

45
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:46,820
to designate a Crown Prince early.

46
00:04:49,140 --> 00:04:50,340
Some said directly that

47
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:54,580
there was a root for our nation.

48
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:57,060
And a Crown Prince was the root.

49
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,540
Without a root,

50
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,540
there would be big trouble.

51
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:05,260
Some resigned and went back to their hometown.

52
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:07,540
They said they were dying

53
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:09,100
and wanted to see the world at peace.

54
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,220
If they could see

55
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:15,100
the Crown Prince was appointed before they died,

56
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:18,020
they would die in peace.

57
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:23,780
Some said I had the virtue to take advice.

58
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:29,140
So, they hesitated a lot

59
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,100
before submitting the proposals,

60
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:32,820
not for fear of punishment,

61
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,620
but for fear of ruining my virtue

62
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:37,300
if I didn’t listen.

63
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:40,820
But for our nation,

64
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:43,660
they still submitted the proposals,

65
00:05:43,660 --> 00:05:44,500
regardless of the inner pain.

66
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:50,060
Sure.

67
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,740
A comet was an anomaly.

68
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:58,340
Because we don’t have a Crown Prince.

69
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:02,220
A flood was the disaster.

70
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,580
Because we don’t have a Crown Prince.

71
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:19,700
There is a flood in the Capital.

72
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:21,940
Houses are ruined and people are drowned.

73
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:24,300
It has never happened before.

74
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,740
Water is the root of everything.

75
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:28,540
The Crown Prince is the root of the world.

76
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,740
Everything in this world

77
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,020
has something to do with the Crown Prince.

78
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:47,300
They’re gentlemen, anyway.

79
00:06:48,060 --> 00:06:50,180
At least, they haven’t pointed at me and said,

80
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:51,900
“You’re the Emperor.

81
00:06:52,460 --> 00:06:53,340
Your priority

82
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:54,740
is to have a son

83
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:55,620
to continue the imperial family.

84
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,100
If you’re not capable enough

85
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:57,940
to have a son,

86
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:58,700
you should designate a son from the clan

87
00:06:58,700 --> 00:06:59,900
as we require.

88
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:01,660
Then we won’t worry if you fall ill

89
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,460
or if you die.”

90
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:03,420
Your Majesty!

91
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:16,740
Your Majesty.

92
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,420
Your Majesty.

93
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:23,020
In my heart,

94
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:25,500
you’re the most important man.

95
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:28,140
You’re millions of times more important

96
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:32,940
than the nation or children.

97
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:37,820
Your Majesty.

98
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,020
Really?

99
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:55,940
If we need a Crown Prince from the imperial clan,

100
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:59,380
Zongshi is the best candidate.

101
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:01,500
You’re his adoptive mother.

102
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,700
You’ll be the Empress Dowager.

103
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:04,900
Your nephew

104
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,580
stole the heart of my only daughter.

105
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:10,780
If I die today...

106
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:11,700
Your Majesty!

107
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:30,780
Why?

108
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:37,500
What have I done wrong?

109
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,700
Why were my children

110
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:45,620
taken away from me

111
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:48,580
one after another?

112
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:53,260
Even Huirou,

113
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:57,860
my only daughter.

114
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:00,780
Now,

115
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:02,820
someone can cheat her to fool me.

116
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:03,820
Your Majesty.

117
00:09:04,340 --> 00:09:06,020
She cares for someone else.

118
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,340
Your Majesty.

119
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:12,540
Your Majesty.

120
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:17,020
If you really suspect us...

121
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:19,740
If you suspect us

122
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:24,580
for colluding and tricking you,

123
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:26,700
kill Cao Ping,

124
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:28,700
kill me,

125
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,180
kill Zongshi,

126
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,140
and kill all my families.

127
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:38,220
But Huirou is your daughter.

128
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,540
Would she ever trick you?

129
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:41,020
Huirou.

130
00:10:42,780 --> 00:10:43,460
Father?

131
00:10:43,460 --> 00:10:44,540
I come to see you.

132
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:47,820
Are you getting better?

133
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:54,460
I don’t want to marry Li Wei.

134
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:10,980
You haven’t eaten anything for long.

135
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,700
Have the congee.

136
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:16,540
Have it before we talk.

137
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,060
Come.

138
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:45,220
I don’t want to marry Li Wei.

139
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:57,060
Li Wei is different from his mother.

140
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,700
Look at his paintings.

141
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:02,500
Can I only

142
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,500
look at his paintings,

143
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:07,620
instead of him?

144
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,700
Can I avoid his mother, too?

145
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,700
Huirou.

146
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:15,820
He’s a good man.

147
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:17,980
He will love you

148
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,660
and protect you all your life.

149
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:35,260
Is he smarter than Her Highness?

150
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:41,740
Is he gentler or kinder than mother?

151
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:45,380
Father.

152
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,340
Why would you

153
00:12:49,420 --> 00:12:51,140
love Madam Zhang?

154
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,180
No,

155
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:56,540
I mean, Empress Wencheng?

156
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:00,220
Why...

157
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:04,460
Why can’t I like Cao Ping?

158
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:18,980
Empress Wencheng loves me sincerely.

159
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,340
Except my true love,

160
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:22,460
she wanted nothing else,

161
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:25,060
regardless of fame, status,

162
00:13:25,060 --> 00:13:26,020
or even life.

163
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,420
Can Cao Ping do that?

164
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:31,660
I can ignore how many women

165
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:33,060
he has messed up with.

166
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,260
Huirou.

167
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:37,100
Within three days,

168
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:38,180
if you can recover,

169
00:13:38,980 --> 00:13:40,300
I’ll

170
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:42,980
give Cao Ping a chance.

171
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:46,340
A chance to choose the future for you and him.

172
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:58,220
Listen carefully.

173
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:01,300
For Huirou,

174
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:03,740
I’m giving you this chance only.

175
00:14:07,860 --> 00:14:09,420
Do you want to marry Huirou?

176
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:12,900
I don’t dare! I don’t dare!

177
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:14,540
I’m sorry.

178
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:16,580
I’m awfully sorry.

179
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:20,380
Don’t you even ask me

180
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:23,060
how you can marry my daughter?

181
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:26,820
Maybe you can do that?

182
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:30,540
Princess is the most honorable girl.

183
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:32,660
I’m too humble

184
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:33,860
to be her husband.

185
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:38,980
Too humble?

186
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,780
Since you know you’re too humble for her,

187
00:14:43,380 --> 00:14:45,020
why did you mess up with her?

188
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:47,180
I...

189
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:49,820
I was young and naive.

190
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:51,660
I was stupid.

191
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:53,220
I overestimated myself.

192
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:55,300
I...

193
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,740
I know I’m wrong.

194
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:00,340
Uncle.

195
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,660
No, Your Majesty.

196
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:08,300
Don’t blame my aunt.

197
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,660
Don’t blame my family.

198
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,820
Don’t blame my younger sister.

199
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:24,060
I haven’t even punished you.

200
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,300
I didn’t flog you or imprison you.

201
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:30,660
Your aunt is safe and sound in her chamber.

202
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,700
I threw your father’s proposal
about self-punishment

203
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:35,060
into the fire pan.

204
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:38,500
What are you crying for?

205
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:48,500
I’m asking you again.

206
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,740
Do you want to marry Huirou?

207
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:02,860
I’m leaving the Capital right away.

208
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:05,860
I won’t influence princess again.

209
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:09,260
I’m leaving the Capital right away.

210
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:12,260
I won’t influence princess again.

211
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:04,980
You saw it.

212
00:17:07,020 --> 00:17:08,460
I didn’t even have a chance

213
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:11,580
to tell him the three conditions

214
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,580
we made yesterday

215
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:15,340
that he couldn’t be an official,

216
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:18,940
he couldn’t have a concubine

217
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,220
and the first son should be surnamed Zhao.

218
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:23,980
Father.

219
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:27,060
I lost.

220
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:33,060
You forced me to see

221
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:37,820
the man I loved wasn’t worth it.

222
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:46,380
Huirou.

223
00:17:47,660 --> 00:17:48,820
Listen to me.

224
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:52,540
In fact, I...

225
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,180
I...

226
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:09,420
Father.

227
00:18:12,860 --> 00:18:13,780
I lost.

228
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,540
But you’re not going to win.

229
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:22,020
If you ruin him,

230
00:18:24,300 --> 00:18:26,260
I’ll kill your only daughter.

231
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:22,980
Your Majesty.

232
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:24,340
I’m not sick.

233
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:41,540
Your Majesty.

234
00:19:43,060 --> 00:19:43,980
Huirou is too naughty.

235
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:45,220
I didn’t teach her well.

236
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:50,460
Forget it.

237
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:55,780
You didn’t tell her I was sick, huh?

238
00:19:57,860 --> 00:19:59,980
After she went back, she lay in bed

239
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:01,460
and fell asleep.

240
00:20:01,980 --> 00:20:03,460
When I heard you didn’t feel well,

241
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:04,540
I came immediately.

242
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:05,940
When I go back,

243
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:07,100
I’ll teach her a lesson.

244
00:20:07,900 --> 00:20:09,460
Is Huaiji with her?

245
00:20:09,540 --> 00:20:10,300
Yes.

246
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:12,020
Huaiji said you asked him to...

247
00:20:16,100 --> 00:20:17,540
You may go back, too.

248
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,380
Ask Huirou to have a good rest.

249
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:25,140
Don’t tell her I’m sick.

250
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,300
This is an order.

251
00:20:30,140 --> 00:20:34,220
Let Huaiji stay with her these days

252
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:37,500
and keep an eye on her.

253
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:41,380
Aye.

254
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:56,980
Shouzhong.

255
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:00,260
Here.

256
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,260
Send a message

257
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:09,020
to get Zhang Maoze back.

258
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:16,620
Aye.

259
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:27,060
Xiao Ye’er.

260
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,340
Is princess still asleep?

261
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:31,700
It’s been more than two hours.

262
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,900
She hasn’t called me yet.

263
00:21:37,260 --> 00:21:38,900
Didn’t you go in and check?

264
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:42,300
No.

265
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:44,540
Princess is always angry lately.

266
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:45,780
I don’t dare to go in.

267
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:55,540
Princess.

268
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:01,780
Princess.

269
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:03,660
I’ve brought you

270
00:22:03,660 --> 00:22:04,620
some honeyed kumquats

271
00:22:04,620 --> 00:22:05,740
that are newly sold on the market.

272
00:22:10,860 --> 00:22:11,580
Princess?

273
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:16,580
Princess...

274
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,260
Princess.

275
00:22:34,260 --> 00:22:35,420
Princess. Princess.

276
00:22:35,780 --> 00:22:37,220
Princess. Come down!

277
00:22:37,380 --> 00:22:38,100
Princess.

278
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:40,434
- Princess. - Princess.

279
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:42,580
- Princess, be a good girl. - Princess.

280
00:22:42,580 --> 00:22:43,740
Come down, Princess!

281
00:22:43,780 --> 00:22:44,775
- Princess. - Princess.

282
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:45,627
Princess.

283
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:46,660
Mr. Liang.

284
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,140
The patrol eunuch found

285
00:22:48,140 --> 00:22:49,340
Princess Fukang had climbed up the rockery.

286
00:22:49,580 --> 00:22:50,620
Seems like she wants to jump off it.

287
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:54,500
We want to go up and stop her,

288
00:22:55,060 --> 00:22:56,180
but we fear she might get more excited

289
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:57,260
and really jump off it.

290
